    {
        "url": "/quotes/henry_giroux_528318",
        "quote": "Angela Davis's legacy as a freedom fighter made her an enemy of the state under the increasingly neoliberal regimes of Nixon, Reagan and J. Edgar Hoover because she understood that the struggle for freedom was not only a struggle for political and individual rights but also for economic rights.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Henry Giroux",
            "url": "/quotes/henry_giroux_528318"
